Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.04,0:00:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems that the engine is working well\Nafter being repaired in Quon city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's doing its work in moving us\Naway from civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are my dear bustling\Nsounds of the city...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We are again immersed in the sounds\Nof rowdy men in a crowded space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again...\NWanna quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.52,0:00:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As if.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as if someone is waiting\Nfor me on land anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... mmm, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Jiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... you seem pretty pumped-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, you got a haircut, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter, right?\NIt was bothersome anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san, there you go snitching\Nfood again...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme some too! Gimme!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of the wind has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna catch the westerly winds\Nand look for dragon shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... from here on out\Nthis is uncharted territory for us as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... could it mean...\Ndanger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it been a single moment aboard\Nwhen we're not exposed to danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you boarded in the best\Npossible moment, Takita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,From this moment on, this ship\Nwill proceed, as planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.63,0:01:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to aim for "the dragon corridor".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.14,0:01:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The possibilities to encounter\Na pod are next to zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And, in the case we do,\Nit'll be a difficult hunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but with our ears and eyes\NI can assure you that we'll manage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If it goes well, we'll make\Na quick buck!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Our time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years do you think\Nwe've been preparing for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. And I beg of you to be\Nsuccessful in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the big\Ninvestment that went into
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:01:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,making this hunt possible\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:02:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we are done with this,\Nthis time we're gonna have our break for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... what a beautiful sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, continue being in a\Ngood mood for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... draking at this high altitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope our hull lasts enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a duel to see who falls apart first:\Nthe ship or us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"The dragon corridor"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The course of the Quin Zaza is now\Ndirected to that special place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They said that it's a dangerous zone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but, instead of cowering, everyone\Nseems to be in high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As for me... I couldn't\Nreally decide at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Capella.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be short sighted\Nbut your skills are the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Short sighted"? That's uncalled for!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So creppy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bridge... don't fail us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we coursing between cliffs\Neven though we're an airship?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We are looking for updrafts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When we find one, we'll go up\Nin no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... are there dragon pods\Nabove the cliffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, above these thick clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:05:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be a migrating pod,\Na "ferry", that only goes through here\Nduring this season.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Should"? That doesn't sound\Nvery reassuring...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... no, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we don't have other option but to\Nbelieve in Crocco-san's calculations and intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as if we came here\Nwith no plan at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... at least we're in better hands\Nthan relying on Gibbs' intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm? Mika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... that means we\Nare on the right trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We caught the updraft!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Any obstacles?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Capella, raise our bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Engine room! Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! At long last!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maximum output, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez... you're too into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't throw us off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time...\NBut we're finally back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Any dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Bridge! Right below us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Capella! Going full starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Berko...\N-Vadakin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pod...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a huge pod of little dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we finally found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... they gathered and formed\Na bubble?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a huge dragon dango!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a "ferry".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what we were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we nailed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It was about time that fortune\Nstarted smiling on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to use anchors\Nand bomb lances on this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you? Think a little\Nabout our prey's size.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,From what we can see, a single\Ndragon is about twice as tall as Gibbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If we shot an anchor or\Nbomb lances at one of those
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you think would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! They would be torn to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't use me in your explanations!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, those little ones are great\Nbecause you can eat the meat on the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinking your teeth directly\Ninto the meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Their tails would go great in a soup too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since\Nwe used that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go! It's pulling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If we tighten the rope so much,\Nwe'll end up losing the prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the rope run till it weakens!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh, it burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hold it with this friction...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita! Pour water on the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 20 meters of rope left!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:08:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika, pull it toward us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll shot a second harpoon at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Use the spear at your feet!\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... you're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She... she fell...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Bridge! Takita has fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop our course inmediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She was clinging on to the dragon,\Nwasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She is gonna be okay, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... almost forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The ointment Nanami-san\Ngave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what is this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to do my best for the ship\Nto find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I learned how\Nto start a fire properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta thank Jiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,With just this, there's not\Ngoing to be enough smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to build up the flame more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... it's suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Return peacefully to the clouds\Nand grant us good winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't\Nhunt you well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, Takita!!\N-Takitaaa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-Takita!!\N-Takitaaa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you can't be for real...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:14:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer us, damn it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita has fallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't land the ship in this\Ntreacherous place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita... shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She was such a good girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say such ominous things!\NWe don't know anything yet for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be faster if I look\Nfor her in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be watching behind you,\Nlet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me with those eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to take its entrails out\Nand cool down its meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't, all of it will go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, go away, anywhere but here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't dissect it well enough\Nwith this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I... can't do anything about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a draker after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, of all times...\Nis when my body starts to tremble?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me rest for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I dozed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where's the little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Heey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez... Don't wander off on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that the presence I sensed\Nwasn't a wild goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That floaty little thing,\Nis that a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Wh- who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You entered someone else's territory\Nwithout even saying hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh??
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:18:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I see\Na dragon alive so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a cub?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm Ascella, a matagi hunter.\N-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,These are my hunting grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... so you were a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be able to tell\Nfrom my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell from a draking vessel\Nwith an injured dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell from the sky\Nand survived?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! What a disaster you went through!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... so that means you're\None of those drakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... do you have a knife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Of course, I'm a matagi hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I tasted dragon meat once before,\Nbut dissecting it is a first for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... this one is rather a small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We call everything a dragon, but\Ntheir types and sizes are very different...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How come it can fly without wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dragon heart"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they have different shapes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All dragons have a heart like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehh? Just with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look very tasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.79,0:19:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, the heart is so\Nhard that it's not edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh! Wai-!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika, we don't have much fuel left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to go back to the ship soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good, the valley is so\Nmuch more complicated than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:19:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we refuel, we're setting out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-No way!\N-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow that! The sun's setting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll set out in this first\Nthing tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs! You know that I can see well\Nin the dark! Let me try once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I can allow that\Nand lose you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... the sun is setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If we continue like this and lose\Nour field of vision, the ship will be in trouble too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Deputy captain, raise our course\Nabove the cliffs
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Following the protocol, we'll declare the next\N48 hours as the search period.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This place has a very complicated terrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lower our course too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue the sailing in zigzag\Nat a low speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocco-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:20:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,fires are not allowed at the bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
